  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"PN6FI3LG\">一体两面</p><p data-pid=\"Sdy6tbhq\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=749022514&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%88%BB%E6%9D%BF%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">刻板印象<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>不仅仅性别会带来，你的外貌，阶层，学历各方面都会导致别人对你先入为主的印象</p><p data-pid=\"7HGC63N8\">这也是为什么很多<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=749022514&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9D%80%E7%8C%AA%E7%9B%98&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">杀猪盘<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>能得逞，就是利用这样的刻板印象植入预期，再收割</p><p data-pid=\"hwEfyQBW\">所以同样的刻板印象，有些人能利用并顺势而为，有些人却要吃刻板印象的亏</p><p data-pid=\"fmvxJbfp\">只能说见仁见智</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
